</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>PSVR 2 體驗影片推出 Resident Evil、The Walking Dead、No Man’s Sky</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/06/03/resident-evil-psvr-2/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=resident-evil-psvr-2</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Lawton]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Fri, 03 Jun 2022 05:24:56 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[遊戲情報]]></category><category><![CDATA[PSVR 2]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1103005</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>&#160; PSVR 2 在幾個月前正式發佈，而早前 Sony 就公開了幾款 PSVR 2 的遊戲體驗影片， [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>PSVR 2 在幾個月前正式發佈，而早前 Sony 就公開了幾款 PSVR 2 的遊戲體驗影片，包括恐佈遊戲 Resident Evil、喪屍遊戲 The Walking Dead、機械人與宇宙戰機射擊遊戲 No Man&#8217;s Sky。</p><p>Resident Evil:Village 將會推出 PSVR 2 遊戲。在 Trailer 看到遊戲內的影片變成了第一身 VR 化，用家的頭部移動會反映在遊戲影片中，當然動作遊戲本身也在 VR 的環境下遊玩。包括在場景內向喪屍射擊，以至是推門內進新房間，都特別有臨場感。</p><p><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_43790"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/s7HijaIITYA?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></p><p>The Walking Dead: Saints and Sinners Retribution 是一款打喪屍遊戲，在一個喪屍化的城市中，尋找生存之道。畫面中可看到喪屍數量特別多，而且可用的武器種類也頗為豐富，值得期待。</p><p><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_85627"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/0QHkarv8Mpw?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></p><p>就影片看到 No Man&#8217;s Sky 是一款宇宙戰機與操作機械人的射擊遊戲。在 PSVR 2 上可得到高清晰的畫面影像，玩家可像跳入戰機、機械人裡面一樣，體驗第一身射擊快感。</p><p><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_48060"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/zS5WJrL8dQY?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></p><p>資料來源：YouTube</p><h2> 最新影片</h2><iframe style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;" id="_ytid_84661" width="590" height="332" data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/?enablejsapi=1&amp;list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl&amp;autoplay=0&amp;cc_load_policy=0&amp;cc_lang_pref=&amp;iv_load_policy=1&amp;loop=0&amp;modestbranding=1&amp;rel=0&amp;fs=1&amp;playsinline=1&amp;autohide=1&amp;theme=light&amp;color=white&amp;controls=0&amp;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen="" data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></p><div class="feedflare">
